{'id': 38174455, 'body': "Thank you so much for taking the time to leave such detailed feedback on your experience with Paired.
We hear that not all relationships are the same, which is why we're currently working on ways to personalize the content users see in the app, to ensure that couples are asked questions that are the most relevant to their relationships. 

If you'd like to share any more thoughts, or if there's anything we can do for you, please email us at support@paired.com 💜", 'modified': '2023-08-08T17:09:19Z'}

{'id': 38528465, 'body': "🥰🥹

Thank you SO much for such a heart-warming review! We're so happy to hear that Paired has helped you get closer to your partner and bridged the distance when you had to move away.

If there's anything else you'd like to share, or if there's anything at all we can do for you, don't hesitate to email us at support@paired.com ", 'modified': '2023-08-25T15:37:43Z'}

{'id': 37824733, 'body': "Thanks a lot for taking the time to share your thoughts with us. We're sorry that you feel like some Daily Questions don't apply to you — reminding you that you can't live together, and hurting your feelings, is the last thing we want! 

Your comments have been shared with the rest of the team and we'll make sure to keep them in mind when creating further content.

If you'd like to share anything else, please get in touch at support@paired.com - we always love to hear from our users!", 'modified': '2023-07-21T15:05:42Z'}

{'id': 32913620, 'body': "Hi there! 

Thanks a lot for taking the time to try the app and leave us a such an extensive review 🙌 We've heard you, and updated the way we display activity in the app. If you update your app, you will see a new Discuss tab which gives you an overview of the content you or your partner recently interacted with. You might also notice that our in-app Chat has moved: now, each conversation has a dedicated Chat section so that you can talk about your answers more easily.

Please don't hesitate to let us know your thoughts regarding this new layout, and feel free to email us at support@paired.com if there's anything you need ✨ ", 'modified': '2022-11-01T17:15:19Z'}

{'id': 28569037, 'body': "Hi Christi, thanks a lot for giving Paired a try and sharing your experience with us! It's a pleasure to hear that the app has been helpful to you and your fiancé, and it created a safe space for him to talk about his feelings.
If you want to reflect on a specific conversation, you can long press on it in the Chat tab and it will offer the option to quote and reply to this particular content. I've also passed on  comments about the Chat to our dedicated team so we can look into improving it further! 

If there's anything else you'd like to share, please feel free to get in touch with us at support@getpaired.com 🙏", 'modified': '2022-03-14T18:05:21Z'}

{'id': 39640066, 'body': "Thank you for taking the time to raise this issue with the app!

We're currently working on adding more personalisation to the app, and one of our goal is to allow couples to exclude content that isn't relevant to them & their relationship. In the meantime, your feedback has been passed on so that we can review our upcoming content with your comment in mind!

If there's anything else we can do for you, don't hesitate to get in touch at support@paired.com!", 'modified': '2023-10-20T15:12:30Z'}

{'id': 39639754, 'body': "Thanks a lot for taking the time to share your thoughts about your experience with Paired!

Your request for a dark mode has been passed on to our dedicated team and we'll consider it as part of our upcoming projects 🙌

As for the lags and freezes when using the app - this shouldn't be happening! We keep making improvements to the performances of the app, but if you can spare the time, we'd like to investigate your situation further. Please email us at support@paired.com with details of what makes the app freeze on your end, and we'll investigate this 🙏", 'modified': '2023-10-20T14:51:55Z'}

{'id': 36665895, 'body': "Hi there! Thanks a lot for taking the time to share your experience with Paired - we're sorry that you've been having issues lately! 

If your app is up to date and you're still encountering freezes and crashes, please email us at support@paired.com with your account details. It will allow us to investigate the situation and offer you more help 💜 

In the meantime, your feedback about Dark Mode has been passed on to our dedicated team and we'll make sure to take it into consideration when reviewing our future projects! 🙏", 'modified': '2023-05-22T16:56:57Z'}

{'id': 35632079, 'body': "Hi there! Thanks for taking the time to try the app.

I'm sorry to hear you were unexpectedly charged following your free trial. Trials started via the App Store and in-app purchases are set to autorenew unless cancelled manually at least 24 hours before they end - this could be why you've been charged for Paired Premium. Don't hesitate to get in touch with Apple support to request a refund if your purchase was made via your Apple ID, and our teams are available to help if you need anything. Feel free to email us at support@paired.com for more guidance on this topic!
", 'modified': '2023-03-28T10:32:44Z'}

